<br>
If any guild WC are interested, e-mail me at didjiman@cs.com; I have an Excel spreadsheet with all recipes, weapon types, etcetera in it, that you can use to figure out exactly how much it costs to make a particular weapon, how much you can salvage from crafter weapons, what the value of the salvage is, and what the loss on each weapon is.  I had to do something while waiting for that little green bar to march across the screen, and this spreadsheet is it.  Requires Excel 2000, and enabled VBA macros.  My request is that you NOT distribute my spreadsheet to anyone outside of guild -- I've got about 40 hours of programming time into it, and I do consider it to be my intellectual property.<br>
